{"tid":1512320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望各位睇一睇。","createTime":"2019-08-28T00:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T00:17:32.000Z","uid":294967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0d74c9f20387628f71b7d339f9d53a297703fce4","tid":1512320,"uid":294967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:03:42.000Z","msg":"見到有個po 講對警察子女的行動以及良心。<br />\n我知道大家對黑警既所作所為好憤怒，但請大家緊記自己既初心。<br />\n我唔係想叫大家畫地為牢。<br />\n我希望大家為自己設定底線，並且堅持。<br />\n<br />\nHe who fights too long against dragons becomes a dragon himself; and if you gaze too long into the abyss, the abyss will gaze into you.<br />\nFriedrich Nietzsche<br />\n<br />\n各位！我地已經失去左好多野。<br />\n但我唔希望各位失去了自己。<br />\n<br />\n有時候妥協好容易，但妥協一次就有下一次。<br />\n<br />\n第一次開Po，原諒我講野1999。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74863286fa2ff81371301060ed9abe567e955f10","tid":1512320,"uid":281342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aV9PDMb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaV9PDMb.jpg&h=367f07d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XK3MFZx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXK3MFZx.jpg&h=6eaec94d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kc4Dw6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKc4Dw6c.jpg&h=8e6229a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PwuzPST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPwuzPST.jpg&h=36f1ffcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c345a4c6d7743fe04bb2e34d1a2aed682e8e4091","tid":1512320,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:17:22.000Z","msg":"美國時間28號<br />\n即係仲有4個鐘就截<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲爭萬幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何君堯果個2日就搞掂<br />\n呢個用左成個月都推唔爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/kni